      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a pretty strong take. I was hoping for a more balanced view for my paper. I mean, some people argue that the intervention was necessary to prevent a massive humanitarian disaster like what was happening in Syria at the time. Even if the aftermath was messy, wasn't there a legitimate case for stopping the imminent massacre in Benghazi?",
